message: Hello! Welcome to Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Hi Chris! I'm a happy customer of Better Deal Insurance. I need help with an issue regarding my policy.
I'm glad to hear you're happy with our service! I'd be happy to help. Before we proceed, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Sure, my name is Sarah Johnson.
Great, thank you for completing security, Sarah. How can I assist you with your policy today?
I recently had an accident and need to make a claim, but I'm encountering some issues with the process.
I'm deeply sorry to hear about your accident, Sarah. Let's see how we can help. Can you also confirm your date of birth for additional checks?
Thank you for providing that, Sarah. I will do my best to assist you. Could you please share the first line of your address and postcode?
Certainly, my address is 123 Oak Street, AB01 2CD.
Thank you for completing security checks, Sarah. I appreciate your cooperation. How can we proceed with your claim issue?
I've been trying to submit the claim online, but the website keeps giving me an error message and won't let me proceed.

I apologize for the inconvenience, Sarah. Let's work together to find a solution. A possible resolution could be to escalate this to our technical team to investigate the website issue. How does that sound?
That works for me, Chris. I appreciate your help in resolving this matter.
I'm glad we could help find a way forward, Sarah. I will escalate this to our technical team for further investigation. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you for your assistance, Chris.
You are welcome, Sarah. If you need any further support, please don't hesitate to reach out. Have a great day!
